<h2 id="how">How does this work?</h2>

<pre><code>X = (fontSizeMax - fontSizeMin) / (viewportWidthMax - viewportWidthMin)

Y = fontSizeMax - viewportWidthMax * X

Z = X * 100

Result = clamp(fontSizeMin, Yrem + Zvw, fontSizeMax)</code></pre>

